This paper discusses the energy efficiency of a wireless network, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, information theory, multimedia, systems, and architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
